div.p: The Error: Calling clone(CLONE_NEWNET) after attempting to move the veth. The Reality: You cannot call ip link set netns <pid> until the container PID is returned by clone(). The Fix: Use a synchronization pipe. Host waits for PID, creates veth, moves end, then signals container to continue.

g.text: run("ip link add veth_h0 type veth peer veth_c0");
run("ip link set veth_c0 netns %d", container_pid);
